                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-6 pt-2">
                    <div class="card about-card">
                        <img class="card-img-top" src="~/Images/thumb-02.jpg">
                        <div class="card-body pt-0 px-0">
                            <div class="about-heading text-white">
                                <span class="font-weight-bold px-2">Transmission</span>
                            </div>
                            <p class="card-text text-left px-2">
                                SNGPL transmission system extends from Sui in Baluchistan to Peshawar in Khyber Pakhtunkhwa (KPK) comprising over 9,106 KM of Transmission System
                            </p>
                            <a asp-action="About" asp-controller="Home" class="btn btn-outline-danger btn-sm mx-2">Read More</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-6 pt-2">
                    <div class="card about-card">
                        <img class="card-img-top" src="~/Images/thumb-03.jpg">
                        <div class="card-body pt-0 px-0">
                            <div class="about-heading text-white">
                                <span class="font-weight-bold px-2">Distribution</span>
                            </div>
                            <p class="card-text text-left px-2">
                                SNGPL's Distribution department is responsible for the safe, reliable and efficient distribution of natural gas through the utility pipes to customers.
                            </p>
                            <a asp-action="About" asp-controller="Home" class="btn btn-outline-danger btn-sm mx-2">Read More</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
